{"h8a051e45g6084g4486gb15cgf74bcff9dc46": ["The Grand Duke could be inside! Don't just stand there - push! ", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "e8baaede-d1f6-8d7c-84e3-af188f7fc1c3"], "ha43c0e31g6ae1g458cg8c77ga18fbe229427": ["There was no Duke inside, just a wood elf. And she's dead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "9076a707-8ba5-11cd-990a-4961bd9eb4dd"], "he05287a1g96a3g40acg8c42gc98a0130855d": ["The counsellor. Gods. We need to get moving, now.", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "648d8087-e53e-1bb6-d1bc-1f40a72f50c1"], "h7964b860g06cbg49ecgabdagbcdcf3e69296": ["What happened to this place?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "647da824-c6cf-f0a7-e562-8070d97b2388"], "h0ac65247g4e71g47ecgac86g284f018d0d6d": ["Goblins and drow happened. ", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "e74ae809-b3d5-8508-fb31-2b0557019d74"], "h0d9eafa1gba87g401fg990dg2023c8226e93": ["Now push, damn it!", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "3c14940c-a3ee-9649-a095-4769d835993a"], "h58f11b59g178cg4c92gb765gfacc8daedddf": ["Who's trapped in there?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "a150a250-e968-597f-c29c-748fb3df7396"], "h7c485852g4f04g4754g9124g374b18f3d75a": ["Your kind happened! ", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "b18aa70b-82af-1738-d7f2-703553fa3cb1"], "hb2575048g57edg472bgb42ege4cc9a478e3e": ["Unless you're here to finish the job, get over here and push!", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "5c70a0cd-652e-2a01-3e42-1004396ef4f8"], "h5acc7e8dg8f08g4f3ag8facgf782bfa3dff7": ["The Grand Duke?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "dcec4553-c7d4-8df8-1711-81f14759d57b"], "h7c2b94b0g476bg44e8ga0b0gda98c5c4dff5": ["Grand Duke Ravengard of Baldur's Gate.", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "f6b04eef-e7e8-c29e-123e-dbefe8a66e32"], "h2d84c5a8gd0e8g4142gbcf0gce3b47f9d658": ["He could be trapped. Help us get through! ", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "effb2803-36d6-7b4d-5d75-29c5c3c027a0"], "h0edc942dgedfeg4c51g8da6ga4dbdffd3d70": ["<i>Push against the wreckage.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "10eb0747-6441-583d-6a33-d8d22f2b5c91"], "h71b11e1bg0874g411ag873fgaa3d860a3d9a": ["Inside, hurry! We don't have much time!", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "7a8945f4-bcf9-0187-de0b-7a848352e04e"], "habef28c8g4ad2g4893g8b9ag1ed55eea19e7": ["Damn. Find another way inside!", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "074755c2-bda7-b812-6ab1-d912ab5f860c"], "h5779829ag65fbg48feg8323g63fcd447410d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "7bf7d3f4-c5d6-b47c-d74d-7246ea81febe"], "h8695ce99g0a60g483aga2ecgb2ef3fb0a4ff": ["Stop staring, start helping!", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "9d522041-6b56-72a9-84d7-9bad34951628"], "h89bfa2d7gbab5g4220gad76gdbd2c6332cd9": ["Go! There has to be another way in!", "646a4195-4091-4dc9-81e1-cff2604f3911", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFists.html", "52056870-b4b7-dcc5-9d1b-d34038dd7ee7"]}